text: Hello Sahra! How are you? I am back from holiday now. How have you been getting on with things?

Hey Chloe! How was your time off? I hope you had a fab time! :sparkles: I have been very busy myself with house renovations this summer so haven’t been doing much animating recently, but I’m thinking of getting back into it soon :’) got an essay to hand in September so that will keep me busy as well :rolling_on_the_floor_laughing:
